How to display, tag and categorise news articles.

## When to use this pattern

Use this pattern to publish a news article to a public-facing website.

## How to use this pattern

### News index

This index sorts the already-published news so that the most recently posted article is at the top of the list.

Use the [articles component](/components/articles) to build consistent summaries of articles.

A list of [categories](/patterns/news/#categories) appears on the news index, and you could also add contact details for the media team. Another optional feature is “[Follow us](/foundations/typography#inline-list-with-icon-prefix)” social media links to Instagram, Facebook, Twitter and LinkedIn.

If you do not include an image with each article, the news index will use a placeholder. Placeholders do not look professional or support the written content to tell a story. The [articles component](/components/articles) has advice on image dimensions.

