### Categories

Allocate at least one category to each news article: either press release or statement. The categories then appear on the news index. A category that has no posts assigned to it will not be visible on the news index. If a user selects a category, it takes them to a news index for all the articles in that category.

Only one category will be visible on the news index, even if the article is assigned to more than one.

